TIMOTHY JORDAN: OK.

00:06:44.530 --> 00:06:48.250
Let me talk a little bit more
about that conversation,

00:06:48.250 --> 00:06:50.350
because I think this is
a really key point.

00:06:50.350 --> 00:06:55.220
So at Google I/O last year, we
had people sign up for what we

00:06:55.220 --> 00:06:58.460
called the Explorer program
and it was a chance to get

00:06:58.460 --> 00:07:01.310
early access to Glass.

00:07:01.310 --> 00:07:03.350
As they came up and they signed
up, we gave them a

00:07:03.350 --> 00:07:05.390
glass bar, something that looked
a little bit like this.

00:07:05.390 --> 00:07:06.570
And I was so excited.

00:07:06.570 --> 00:07:07.410
They gave me one, too.

00:07:07.410 --> 00:07:09.955
This is mine and I'm
number 2182.

00:07:09.955 --> 00:07:12.100
It's a high number, I know.

00:07:12.100 --> 00:07:16.040
I went home and I took a photo
of this glass bar and I put it

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:16.830
on Google+.

00:07:16.830 --> 00:07:18.310
I posted it to all my friends.

00:07:18.310 --> 00:07:20.860
I posted it publicly so that
everybody could see how

00:07:20.860 --> 00:07:22.520
excited I was.

00:07:22.520 --> 00:07:23.300
And it was interesting.

00:07:23.300 --> 00:07:25.500
This weird thing happened right
after that-- we started

00:07:25.500 --> 00:07:29.240
seeing a whole bunch of these
photos go up, and people were

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:30.380
doing this crazy thing.

00:07:30.380 --> 00:07:33.450
They weren't just taking a photo
of the bar or talking

00:07:33.450 --> 00:07:34.680
about the Explorer program--

00:07:34.680 --> 00:07:37.040
they put the bar out there where
they live and took a

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:41.110
photo, or in front of the people
that they love, or in

00:07:41.110 --> 00:07:45.110
front of things that they care
about, or the places that made

00:07:45.110 --> 00:07:46.360
them feel home.

00:07:49.480 --> 00:07:51.620
And it was then that we started
to figure out that

00:07:51.620 --> 00:07:54.020
this was more than just
a group of people

00:07:54.020 --> 00:07:56.810
signing up for a device.

00:07:56.810 --> 00:07:58.060
It was a bunch of people
that wanted

00:07:58.060 --> 00:07:59.380
to be part of something.

00:08:02.350 --> 00:08:02.470
OK.

