00:31:46.885 --> 00:31:50.330
know, "The New York Times" is
a leading global multimedia

00:31:50.330 --> 00:31:52.292
information company.

00:31:52.292 --> 00:31:54.790
It enhances society by creating
and collecting and

00:31:54.790 --> 00:31:57.540
