00:32:09.910 --> 00:32:11.940
and read a newspaper.

00:32:11.940 --> 00:32:14.690
What really works for me and
what we found is a great

00:32:14.690 --> 00:32:17.905
experience on Glass is getting
headlines throughout the day

00:32:17.905 --> 00:32:21.500
that are there whenever
I look for them.

00:32:21.500 --> 00:32:22.390
And that's what we built.

00:32:22.390 --> 00:32:26.590
Let's take a look at what
that looks like.

00:32:26.590 --> 00:32:30.030
So here is a bundle of news that
