00:32:39.170 --> 00:32:40.520
corner there, that fold.

00:32:40.520 --> 00:32:47.810
If I tap on this item, I get a
bundle of all these different

00:32:47.810 --> 00:32:49.490
headlines and rich images.

00:32:52.800 --> 00:32:57.440
And if I tap on any one of
these, I can get a card option

00:32:57.440 --> 00:32:58.690
for read aloud.

00:33:02.570 --> 00:33:04.250
So this is really great
for me, actually,

00:33:04.250 --> 00:33:05.500
because I can hear it.

00:33:09.001 --> 00:33:10.750
Uh huh.

